        <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI">https://www.era.europa.eu/system/files/2023-05/esc-rsc_technical_document_en.pdf</rdfs:seeAlso>
        <ns1:term_status>stable</ns1:term_status>
        <skos:note xml:lang="en">Harmonised restriction code 2.4.20 (if Class A radio system is installed, so not `era-rscv-eratv:not-applicable` nor `era-rscv-rinf:10`).</skos:note>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">Information on RSC voice requirements per country is given in the referred document.

Vehicles are considered compatible with the infrastructure regarding this parameter, if any of the values declared matches.
In case the value “Not Defined” or “RSC-EU-0” is used, repetitions with additional values are not expected.</skos:scopeNote>
