        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">Only applicable for Traction Locomotives, which are intended to detect derailments or precursors to derailments in freight wagons hauled by the locomotive, with equipment fulfilling this function shall be located entirely on board the locomotive.</skos:scopeNote>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


