EN 13803:2017, Tables N.A and N.2</rdfs:seeAlso>
        <ns1:term_status>stable</ns1:term_status>
        <skos:altLabel xml:lang="en">ERATV: Radius of the smallest horizontal curve capability of the vehicle, expressed in metres.</skos:altLabel>
