        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Declares whether a national registration property concept is mandatory for the member state context where it applies. This property is asserted on SKOS Concepts in the NationalRegistrationProperties concept scheme and is used by SHACL constraints to verify presence of required national properties.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:isDefinedBy rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/949/"/>
