        <terms:modified rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2024-09-19</terms:modified>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Part of the End of tunnel that indicates the km of the line at the end of a tunnel.
The End of tunnel is the Geographical coordinates in decimal degrees and km of the line at the end of a tunnel. The reason for deprecation is that the property is now a subproperty of lineReference in order to represent the kilometer in relation to a national railway line</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:isDefinedBy rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/949/"/>
